					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">One thing I like about the MMC5 is that you have IRQs yet still can switch the entire CHR-ROM range with a single write. Very useful for clean screen splits and elaborate status bars with sprites in them. On the MMC3 with its stupid index register, changing the entire 8 KiB takes an eternity.</div>

