						<div class="postbody">As I see it, this is a chicken vs. egg situation... The hardware people don't want to make a complex, expensive board since there's nothing interesting to put on it (licenced or homebrew), and programmers don't want to code MMC5 software because there's no hardware where to put it.</div>

